</ref><ref name="eentertainment">{{cite news|last=Ryan|first=Joel|title="The Closet," the Controversy--and Cruise|work=[[E! Online]]|publisher=E! Entertainment Television, Inc.|date=[[2006-03-13]]|url=http://www.eonline.com/news//article/index.jsp?uuid=9495664b-650c-4ae8-8a37-5dbf15296d80&entry=index|accessdate=2007-06-16}}</ref> These assertions were soon also reported by ''[[E! News]]'' and ''[[American Morning]]''.<ref name="eentertainment" /><ref>{{cite news 
