</ref>  ''[[FOX News]]'' attributed threats from Tom Cruise, stating, "to back out of his "Mission: Impossible III" promotional duties if Viacom didn<U+2019>t pull a repeat of the episode," as evidence of "bad blood" between Cruise and Viacom.<ref>{{cite news 
